    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li>将tomcat-jdbc导出jar包，添加到Tomcat\lib,删除原来tomcat-jdbc.jar包。</li></ul><hr><ul><li><p>生成加密字符串[]里的内容，进入Tomcat\lib目录执行命令（XXX为要加密的字符串）。<br> <code>java -cp datasource.jar com.datasource.security.encrypt.CipherEncrypter XXX</code></p></li><li><p>修改context.xml中username、url、password为加密后的密文。</p></li><li><p>如果需要修改其他版本的tomcat找到对应版本的tomcat-jdbc源码</p><ul><li>添加CipherEncrypter类。</li><li>按需修改DataSourceFactory.java中对应设置username、url、password方法。  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line"> value = properties.getProperty(PROP_PASSWORD);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (value != <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    poolProperties.setPassword(CipherEncrypter.decrypt(value));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">value = properties.getProperty(PROP_URL);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (value != <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    poolProperties.setUrl(CipherEncrypter.decrypt(value));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">value = properties.getProperty(PROP_USERNAME);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (value != <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    poolProperties.setUsername(CipherEncrypter.decrypt(value));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>context.xml文件中配置<br><code>factory=&quot;org.apache.tomcat.jdbc.pool.DataSourceFactory&quot;</code></p></li><li>当前源码对应版本apache-tomcat-7.0.82</li></ul>]]></content>
    
